Text: WisdomTree U.S. Total Market Fund (NYSEARCA:EXT) to Issue $0.18  -  Dividend WisdomTree U.S. Total Market Fund (NYSEARCA:EXT) declared a  -  dividend on Tuesday, September 24th, Wall Street Journal reports. Shareholders of record on Wednesday, September 25th will be paid a dividend of 0.18 per share by the exchange traded fund on Friday, September 27th. This represents a yield of 2%.
